name: codyshreed
description: At the end of 2017 I sat down with some great friends and we decided to all share our goals/resolutions for 2018. I've always been a goals-oriented person, but rarely have I ever shared them this openly, and I must admit there was something powerful about it. I think the magic in knowing that others are aware of your intentions is in the accountability it creates - your goals are now in the open and you have friends that want to see you succeed, and if you let yourself down you let them down too.
